  "prompt": "When is the new MacBook Pro rumored to release?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, Apple has not officially announced the release date for the next MacBook Pro. However, industry rumors and analyst predictions suggest that a new MacBook Pro model could be unveiled either in late 2023 or during Apple's early 2024 product events. These potential updates might include advancements such as the next generation of Apple\u2019s M-series processors (like the rumored M3 chip), improved display technologies, and other hardware enhancements.\n\nIt's always a good idea to keep an eye on official Apple announcements or trusted technology news sources for the most accurate and up-to-date information regarding product releases.",
